<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:08:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军方称，哈马斯在加沙扣押了 222 名人质，其中包括“相当多”外国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</link><description>美国报道称，拜登政府建议以色列推迟对加沙的地面入侵，以方便人质获释 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，自周日以来，以色列对加沙的袭击已造成 400 人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军表示，已通知 222 名人质家属，其中包括“不少”外国人■ 以色列国防军袭击真主党据点，北部边境局势再度紧张 ■ 第三批前往加沙的援助物资经埃及进入拉法过境点 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：4,380 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，13,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，以色列正奔向道德深渊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</guid></item><item><title>15万枚导弹瞄准以色列：真主党的致命武器库能达到多远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有深入以色列境内的火箭和远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 07:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势加剧，以色列军队等待入侵加沙的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-awaits-order-for-gaza-invasion-as-middle-east-tensions-sear/0000018b-58f5-dd05-a7bf-ffffe0550000</link><description>随着伊朗试图针对以色列和美国的利益、也门叛乱分子向以色列发射导弹以及真主党使边境升温，美国在该地区部署了大量军事存在。内塔尼亚胡的圈子传达的信息是，最好不要急于进入加沙，担心发生大规模火灾</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 05:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-awaits-order-for-gaza-invasion-as-middle-east-tensions-sear/0000018b-58f5-dd05-a7bf-ffffe0550000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5a6c-d473-a5fb-7eedd9540000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 02:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5a6c-d473-a5fb-7eedd9540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医疗队提供哈马斯屠杀细节以进行战争罪调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-medical-teams-provide-details-of-hamas-massacre-for-war-crimes-probes/0000018b-58c8-d8e2-a1eb-fbde4cc50000</link><description>扎卡身份识别、撤离和救援志愿者是 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后第一批到达加沙边境地区的志愿者，他们的证词可用于针对以色列和国外恐怖分子的刑事案件</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 00:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-medical-teams-provide-details-of-hamas-massacre-for-war-crimes-probes/0000018b-58c8-d8e2-a1eb-fbde4cc50000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，土地又恢复混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/and-in-israel-the-land-returns-to-chaos/0000018b-58aa-