b-fbf6ae0a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 23:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-23/ty-article/go-home-gal-hirsch-israel-needs-someone-capable-of-the-job/0000018b-58e4-d8e2-a1eb-fbf6ae0a0000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡和他的亲信来说，生与死只是拍照而已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-22/ty-article/.highlight/for-netanyahu-and-his-cronies-life-and-death-are-just-a-photo-op/0000018b-5857-d2b2-addf-7e7f71dc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他任命的人质和失踪人员协调员加尔·赫希无法面对现实。这就是为什么他们不给我们任何希望</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 20:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-22/ty-article/.highlight/for-netanyahu-and-his-cronies-life-and-death-are-just-a-photo-op/0000018b-5857-d2b2-addf-7e7f71dc0000</guid></item><item><title>研究人员推断，西班牙的尼安德特人引发了火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</link><description>我们知道古人类使用火已有数十万年，甚至超过一百万年，但他们能点燃火吗？尼安德特人可以</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</guid></item><item><title>数千名艺术界人士发出信函谴责以色列，但没有提及哈马斯的大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</link><description>艺术家、画廊主和其他艺术界成员发表了这封公开信，其中展示了一位嘲笑以色列人质的艺术家的作品。超过 2000 名艺术家（其中大多数是以色列人）回应道：“你让我们所有人失去人性”</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境社区的幸存者对政府代表不请自来访问他们的基布兹感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/survivors-in-israeli-border-community-angered-by-uninvited-visits-by-govt-reps/0000018b-57b0-d2b2-addf-77f818d90000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的一名居民表示，“他们知道我们不希望他们来，但他们还是来了。”哈马斯 10 月 7 日的残酷袭击造成至少 112 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 17:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/survivors-in-israeli-border-community-angered-by-uninvited-visits-by-govt-reps/0000018b-57b0-d2b2-addf-77f818d90000</guid></item><item><title>国防官员担心内塔尼亚胡任命的负责加沙以色列人质的人可能会损害家人的信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-netanyahus-appointee-on-gaza-hostages-could-harm-families-trust/0000018b-57f8-d8e2-a1eb-f7fe8cb50000</link><description>国防部消息人士批评加尔·赫希与哈马斯最近释放的两名人质合影的决定以及他上周对外国大使的长篇大论</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 17:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-netanyahus-appointee-on-gaza-hostages-could-harm-families-trust/0000018b-57f8-d8e2-a1eb-f7fe8cb50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质：从以色列被绑架的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，超过 200 人——以色列人和非以色列人、婴儿、妇女和老人、平民和士兵——被哈马斯恐怖分子俘虏，并被武力带到加沙。以下是所有经官方确认的人质姓名</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙长达16年的封锁失败了。这真的是唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</link><description>许多以色列分析人士一致认为，封锁加沙是对付哈马斯的唯一途径。但 10 月 7 日的灾难性袭击引发了严峻的问题：封锁政策是否是以色列的另一个重要战略误解</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</guid></item><item><title>“携带枪支，这是救星：本格维尔和他的妻子吹嘘以色列携带武器的人数急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</link><description>上周，以色列议会国家安全委员会批准了国家安全部长本-格维尔提出的枪支许可证规定修正案，以便在南部战事持续不断的情况下，获得许可证的条件更加宽松</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员警告以色列-加沙战争中中东局势升级的可能性增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀和国务卿安东尼·布林肯认为“局势可能会大幅升级”，担心真主党和伊朗可能与以色列发生直接冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>